  <description><![CDATA[<p>You will be met with a warm welcome in the comfortable Hotel Arlberg in <a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855}" title="St Anton">St. Anton</a> by the charming Ennemoser family. </p>
<h2>Family run hotel</h2>
<p><span>Operated by the Ennemoser family for generations, the Arlberg embodies genuine Austrian hospitality. You can expect a warm reception upon your arrival and attentive service during meal times.</span></p>
<h2><span>Bar &amp; relaxation</span></h2>
<p>The hotel offers a home-from-home atmosphere and excellent leisure facilities including an indoor swimming pool and a whirlpool.</p>
<p>The authentically Austrian reception with connecting bar is the perfect place to grab a drink and relax.</p>
<h2><span>Peaceful location</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel's prime location hits the mark as well, just a brief stroll from the Nasserein gondola and the town centre. You can catch the ski bus stop directly outside the hotel entrance. </span></p>
<p><span>You are still sufficiently distanced from the lively centre of St Anton for a bit of peace and quiet in the evenings.</span></p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p>Service- We value the great partnerships we have with our hotels and our longstanding relationship with the Hotel Arlberg means we know you are getting the very best on your Inghams holiday.</p>
<p>Location - The hotel is close to both the Nasserein gondola and the centre of town, while still being in a peaceful location.</p>
<p>Wellness area - An indoor swimming pool and sauna are the perfect place to relax after a day on the slopes.</p>]]></description>
